      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, reflects a standard of care synonymous with collector-grade assets. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise.",
