    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've gotta see this absolute beauty! I've babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a scratch, dent, or worry in sight\u2014it\u2019s in truly pristine condition! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one. It's super clean, super smooth, and ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
