      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept spotless inside and out. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how perfect it is. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions!",
